THE angry family of Kedibone Tau (26) claim she was injected against her will and died as a result. On 13 September, Kedibone from Mazista outside Swartruggens, went into labour. She was taken by ambulance to the Swartruggens Health Centre and then transferred to Job Shimankane Tabane Hospital in Rustenburg, North West. A doctor allegedly wanted to inject her in her spinal cord but Kedibone refused.if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjst7fRIZshpXbxC-Q91kQ8fpaQZNekKz_z2YDQxfRqqDl8LuIEdWrKw8I7LmtCAtClGkZD4rtnGD19kLE7T1zEnj17Pwcw6WciLtp25XOXf5VUh3nH6Yz0mcZlrCO-1Lk1I_BCL5FBpbamy6TI46c5Rb_1cxU7DyRNYzZ0ANVwHhSNf390Xjo9r03Y4LHXAU7m2ojQwooWm-RAQn-0jUM7SeTQ5PAkcpu6z0J-11J3Us2zO2EPq-MUmcQ5phXIBMYrslr0v98TDzWkiebGKZpNYPR5bJ_yk\x26sai\x3dAMfl-YQxd83NHdn5ZuDUHkLHMu3vTLDVkPWVcBAHmpkG-h77fUVhDZSFeCNK_3PDcdsZGCOd1fABg0q5beWOzGg3pR62OE950oqdg0TOqURp\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzK-no5oQ2qXcEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
